    {
      "id": "9IbO-mUR3LKVVb41DloyH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 469.5555555555561,
      "y": 1974.0555447604922,
      "width": 1099.599609375,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aa",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 662605364,
      "version": 1396,
      "versionNonce": 895110668,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774157869945,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "rule1 (the wg disguise SNAT): \n-s 10.10.10.0/24 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n所有source ip是10.10.10.0/24网段的，并且走tailscale0接口出去的包，发出去的时候改source ip为wg server tailscale ip\nCommand: sudo iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 10.10.10.0/24 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n\nrule2 (the rerouter DNAT): \n-d 10.10.10.26 -j DNAT --to-destination 100.83.145.111\n所有dest ip是10.10.10.26的包，发出去的时候改dest ip为100.83.145.111\nCommand: sudo iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -d 10.10.10.26 -j DNAT --to-destination 100.83.145.111\n\nrule3 (the universal disguise SNAT): \n-d 100.83.145.111 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n所有dest ip是100.83.145.111并且要走tailscale0出去的包，发出去的时候source ip改给wg server tailscale ip\nCommand: sudo iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -d 100.83.145.111 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "rule1 (the wg disguise SNAT): \n-s 10.10.10.0/24 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n所有source ip是10.10.10.0/24网段的，并且走tailscale0接口出去的包，发出去的时候改source ip为wg server tailscale ip\nCommand: sudo iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 10.10.10.0/24 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n\nrule2 (the rerouter DNAT): \n-d 10.10.10.26 -j DNAT --to-destination 100.83.145.111\n所有dest ip是10.10.10.26的包，发出去的时候改dest ip为100.83.145.111\nCommand: sudo iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -d 10.10.10.26 -j DNAT --to-destination 100.83.145.111\n\nrule3 (the universal disguise SNAT): \n-d 100.83.145.111 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n所有dest ip是100.83.145.111并且要走tailscale0出去的包，发出去的时候source ip改给wg server tailscale ip\nCommand: sudo iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -d 100.83.145.111 -o tailscale0 -j MASQUERADE\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
